.\" Man page for arachna
.TH ARACHNA 1 "2026-06-09" "arachna 3.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
arachna \- context collector for AI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B arachna
.I command
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B arachna \-\-version
.SH DESCRIPTION
arachna collects project files into token-limited chunks ready for AI consumption.
It understands tokens (not lines) and splits output smartly so nothing gets cut
in the middle.
.PP
It supports incremental diffs via snapshots: snapshot what an AI has seen,
then send only what changed. Works across multiple chats, agents, and sessions.
.PP
Plugins add language-specific features: tree-sitter structural diff for
JavaScript/TypeScript/Go, tiktoken/transformers for accurate token counting.
Core stays zero-dependency.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
\fBcollect\fR
Collect project context.
.TP
\fBcollect \-\-profile\fR \fIname\fR
Collect a specific profile.
.TP
\fBcollect \-\-all\fR
Collect all profiles.
.TP
\fBcollect \-\-list\fR
List available profiles.
.TP
\fBcollect \-\-validate\fR
Validate configuration for errors. Exits 1 if problems found.
.TP
\fBcollect \-\-clean\fR
Remove all collected files.
.TP
\fBsnapshot\fR
Manage snapshots.
.TP
\fBsnapshot list\fR
List all snapshots.
.TP
\fBsnapshot create \-\-profile\fR \fIname\fR \fB\-\-name\fR \fIid\fR
Create a named snapshot.
.TP
\fBsnapshot update\fR \fIid\fR [\fB\-\-profile\fR \fIname\fR]
Update an existing snapshot.
.TP
\fBsnapshot delete\fR \fIid\fR
Delete a snapshot.
.TP
\fBsnapshot info\fR \fIid\fR
Show snapshot details.
.TP
\fBsnapshot rename\fR \fIold\fR \fInew\fR
Rename a snapshot.
.TP
\fBdiff\fR
Diff from the single available snapshot (auto-select).
.TP
\fBdiff \-\-from\fR \fIid\fR
Diff from a specific snapshot.
.TP
\fBdiff \-\-from\fR \fIA\fR \fB\-\-to\fR \fIB\fR
Cross-snapshot diff.
.TP
\fBdiff \-\-all\fR \fB\-\-profile\fR \fIname\fR
Full project as diff.
.TP
\fBstore stats\fR
Show content-addressable store statistics.
.TP
\fBstore gc\fR
Garbage collect unreferenced objects.
.TP
\fBplugins\fR
Plugin management.
.TP
\fBplugins list\fR
List available plugins and their status.
.TP
\fBplugins install\fR \fIlanguage\fR
Install plugin for a language (javascript, typescript, go, tiktoken).
.TP
\fBplugins install\fR \fIlanguage\fR \fB\-\-execute\fR
Install and automatically execute the install command.
.TP
\fBplugins uninstall\fR \fIlanguage\fR
Show uninstall instructions for a plugin.
.TP
\fBpresets update\fR [\fB\-\-url\fR \fIurl\fR]
Update presets from remote repository.
.TP
\fBdoctor\fR
Run configuration diagnostic.
.TP
\fBinit\fR
Interactive .arachna.json bootstrap.
.TP
\fBinit \-\-defaults\fR
Auto-detect project type and create config non-interactively.
.TP
\fBinit \-\-preset\fR \fIname\fR
Use a specific preset for initialization.
.TP
\fBinit \-\-install\-hook\fR
Install post-commit git hook.
.TP
\fBcompletion\fR \fIbash|zsh\fR
Generate shell completion script.
.SH PLUGINS
Plugins add language-specific features without adding dependencies to core.
Install via pip extras or the plugin manager.
.PP
Available plugins:
.TS
tab(;);
l l.
javascript;Tree-sitter structural diff for JavaScript
typescript;Tree-sitter structural diff for TypeScript
go;Tree-sitter structural diff for Go
tiktoken;Accurate token counting for OpenAI models
.TE
.PP
Install: \fBpip install arachna[javascript]\fR
.br
Or: \fBarachna plugins install javascript \-\-execute\fR
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Create a config with auto-detected profiles:
.RS
.B arachna init \-\-defaults
.RE
.PP
Collect all profiles:
.RS
.B arachna collect \-\-all
.RE
.PP
Install JavaScript plugin:
.RS
.B arachna plugins install javascript \-\-execute
.RE
.PP
Create a snapshot and diff later:
.RS
.B arachna snapshot create \-\-profile full \-\-name baseline
.br
.I ... make changes ...
.br
.B arachna diff \-\-from baseline
.RE
.SH FILES
.TP
\fI.arachna.json\fR
Project configuration with profiles.
.TP
\fIarachna_context/\fR
Default output directory for collected files.
.TP
\fI.arachna/\fR
Content-addressable store for Watch snapshots (auto-gitignored).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
0
Success.
.TP
1
Error.
